r results\nwith other works that have analyzed the same datasets, we conclude that this\ntool gives results in agreement with the published results within 1$\\sigma$\nmost of the time, while extracting, with SLOPpy, the planetary signal with a\nsimilar or higher statistical significance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Aug 2022 16:07:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
