 LTE, heterogeneous LTE-Advanced networks, and\nhow traffic is classified within a packet scheduling architecture for\nheterogeneous LTE-Advanced networks. Then, by summarising the proposed\nQoS-based packet scheduling algorithms in the literature for heterogeneous\nLTE-Advanced Networks, and for Femtocells LTE-Advanced Networks. And finally,\nwe provide some concluding remarks in the last section.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Aug 2022 16:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
