strates the synergy\nbetween ALMA and JWST to study the properties of the first galaxies, although\nJWST/NIRSpec spectroscopy will be necessary to confirm or reject the high\nphotometric-redshift of GLASS-z13.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Aug 2022 18:57:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 09:50:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 14:50:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
