We conduct extensive\nexperiments on both real and synthetic datasets, and the results show that our\nalgorithm is up to four orders of magnitude faster than all baselines and\nfinding MaxBPs works better than finding all MBPs for a fraud detection\napplication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Aug 2022 12:18:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-30"}
