.75$, and $\\nu_{3D}=0.58$). When EV particles are\nadded into the system, our results indicate that the crowding density either\ndoes not or only weakly affects the universal scaling relations. We discuss the\nimplications of these results in living matter by showing the experimental\nresult for a dsDNA onto the master plot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 28 Aug 2022 15:27:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 16:14:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
